    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319520/extras/5e1161f4140b173c35a1efc0d10b1818.poster.avif?t=1730531495\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319520/extras/5e1161f4140b173c35a1efc0d10b1818.webm?t=1730531495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319520/extras/5e1161f4140b173c35a1efc0d10b1818.mp4?t=1730531495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOIR BUNKER is an isometric pixel art puzzle-thriller set in a tense, atmospheric world. Navigate the cold, foggy depths of a dark bunker, where every choice you make can either save or doom you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319520/extras/363706328a8107ea07f894cf2674dbd0.poster.avif?t=1730531495\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319520/extras/363706328a8107ea07f894cf2674dbd0.webm?t=1730531495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319520/extras/363706328a8107ea07f894cf2674dbd0.mp4?t=1730531495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319520/extras/dd43e8fe8377359b34ab43e28e960e83.poster.avif?t=1730531495\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319520/extras/dd43e8fe8377359b34ab43e28e960e83.webm?t=1730531495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319520/extras/dd43e8fe8377359b34ab43e28e960e83.mp4?t=1730531495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TWO DISTINCT CONTROL SYSTEMS. Experience the game through either Tank Controls for strategic, fixed-camera precision or Free Camera Controls for a broader, dynamic exploration.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PSYCHOLOGICAL HORROR AND INTENSE PUZZLES. Unravel the dark mysteries hidden within the bunker’s eerie corridors, where every shadow conceals a riddle, and each decision demands a sacrifice.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IMMERSIVE NOIR VISUALS. Dive into a world of stunning pixel art with a noir aesthetic, designed to draw you deeper into its unsettling atmosphere.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >STRATEGIC OBJECT INTERACTIONS. Simple objects like a chair become pivotal; will it be your refuge or the key to deeper despair? Every interaction has consequences.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DYNAMIC CAMERA ANGLES. Switch between fixed and free camera perspectives, each offering unique challenges and intensifying the game’s tension.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DARK AND ATMOSPHERIC SETTING. Explore a meticulously crafted bunker where every corner, every room is filled with a sense of dread, and where every action carries a heavy cost.</p></li></ul>",
